    %% Internal flows
    Evaluator -->|orchestrates| Registry
    Registry -->|resolves| TaskAPI
    Registry -->|resolves| ModelAPI
    ModelAPI -->|interface for| Models
    Evaluator -->|runs| TaskDefs
    Evaluator -->|applies| Filters
    Evaluator -->|uses| Caching
    TaskDefs -->|computes via| BundledMetrics
    TaskDefs -->|custom tasks| Unitxt

    %% External integrations
    LMESOperator["TrustyAI LMEval Service<br/>(lmes-operator)"] -->|creates Job using<br/>container image| LMEvalJob

    %% Egress connections
    HF -->|PyTorch in-process| LocalGPU["Local GPU/CPU"]
    VLLM -->|vLLM engine| LocalGPU
    OpenAI -->|HTTP/HTTPS| InferenceEndpoint["Model Inference Endpoint<br/>(KServe/vLLM Serving)"]
    WatsonX -->|HTTPS/443| WatsonXAPI["IBM watsonx.ai API"]
    AnthropicM -->|HTTPS/443| AnthropicAPI["Anthropic API"]
    Evaluator -->|HTTPS/443| HFHub["HuggingFace Hub"]
    Evaluator -->|Filesystem| PVC["PVC Model Cache"]
    Evaluator -->|Filesystem| OutputDir["Output Directory"]

